0:04:23.980,0:04:37.260
Tunamhuzunisha Roho Mtakatifu kwa kiburi chetu na sisi tunaelezea kiburi chetu kwa njia tofauti.

0:04:37.260,0:04:42.760
Kila mtu anajua kwamba mtu akiwa na kiburi anaonekana hivi.

0:04:42.760,0:04:44.960
